com.usebottles.bottles (2021.7.28-treviso) precise; urgency=low

  * Support for .lnk files
  * Run any .exe/.msi/.lnk using the flags -e/-l in command line
  * Specify the target bottle using the -b flag in command line
  * Run executables without show the Bottles Window
  * Fix crash log path on Flatpak
  * Fixed an issue causing Bottles to detect downloaded dxvk even when it fails
  * Disable uninstaller button for dependencies installed from cab files
  * Warning for missing cabextract tool
  * Several improvements in runner management
  * Added icons to the sidebar
  * Chinese (Simplified) translations thanks to @Yuzaihhhh and @sr093906
  * Japanese translations thanks to @jatin-cbs
  * Hungarian translations thanks to @ovari


